title: Diving at the 2018 European Aquatics Championships – Mixed 3 m springboard synchro
summary: The Mixed 3 m springboard synchro competition of the 2018 European Aquatics Championships was held on 8 August 2018.
content:
The Mixed 3 m springboard synchro competition of the 2018 European Aquatics Championships was held on 8 August 2018.


== Results ==
The final was started at 13:30.
